@startuml
' https://plantuml.com/sequence-diagram

title AnnotationConfigApplicationContext 注解容器启动调用逻辑图
autonumber

actor Client
participant "AnnotationConfigApplicationContext" as ACC
participant "AnnotatedBeanDefinitionReader" as Reader
participant "ClassPathBeanDefinitionScanner" as Scanner
participant "AnnotationConfigUtils" as Utils
participant "DefaultListableBeanFactory\n/ BeanDefinitionRegistry" as Registry
participant "AbstractApplicationContext" as AAC
participant "PostProcessorRegistrationDelegate" as Delegate
participant "ConfigurationClassPostProcessor" as CCPP
participant "ConfigurationClassParser" as Parser
participant "ConfigurationClassBeanDefinitionReader" as ConfigReader

== 构造阶段：初始化 Reader / Scanner / 基础注解处理器 ==

Client -> ACC: new AnnotationConfigApplicationContext()
activate ACC
ACC -> Reader: new AnnotatedBeanDefinitionReader(this)
activate Reader
Reader -> Utils: registerAnnotationConfigProcessors(registry)
activate Utils
Utils -> Registry: set DependencyComparator
Utils -> Registry: set AutowireCandidateResolver
Utils -> Registry: registerBeanDefinition(\nConfigurationClassPostProcessor)
Utils -> Registry: registerBeanDefinition(\nAutowiredAnnotationBeanPostProcessor)
Utils -> Registry: registerBeanDefinition(\nCommonAnnotationBeanPostProcessor?)
Utils -> Registry: registerBeanDefinition(\nPersistenceAnnotationBeanPostProcessor?)
Utils -> Registry: registerBeanDefinition(\nEventListenerMethodProcessor)
Utils -> Registry: registerBeanDefinition(\nDefaultEventListenerFactory)
deactivate Utils
deactivate Reader
ACC -> Scanner: new ClassPathBeanDefinitionScanner(this)
deactivate ACC

note right of Utils
这里注册的是 Spring 处理注解所需的基础设施 BeanDefinition。
最关键的是 ConfigurationClassPostProcessor：
它会在 refresh() 阶段继续解析 @Configuration、@Bean、@Import、@ComponentScan。
end note

== 方式一：通过配置类初始化 ==

Client -> ACC: new AnnotationConfigApplicationContext(AppConfig.class)
activate ACC
ACC -> ACC: this()
ACC -> ACC: register(componentClasses)
ACC -> Reader: register(componentClasses)
activate Reader
loop each componentClass
	Reader -> Reader: registerBean(componentClass)
	Reader -> Reader: doRegisterBean(...)
	Reader -> Registry: registerBeanDefinition(beanName, abd)
end
deactivate Reader
ACC -> ACC: refresh()
deactivate ACC

== 方式二：通过包扫描初始化 ==

Client -> ACC: new AnnotationConfigApplicationContext("com.example")
activate ACC
ACC -> ACC: this()
ACC -> ACC: scan(basePackages)
ACC -> Scanner: scan(basePackages)
activate Scanner
Scanner -> Scanner: doScan(basePackages)
loop each candidate component
	Scanner -> Scanner: findCandidateComponents(basePackage)
	Scanner -> Scanner: postProcessBeanDefinition(...)
	Scanner -> Scanner: processCommonDefinitionAnnotations(...)
	Scanner -> Registry: registerBeanDefinition(beanName, bd)
end
opt includeAnnotationConfig == true
	Scanner -> Utils: registerAnnotationConfigProcessors(registry)
	Utils -> Registry: register infrastructure BeanDefinitions
end
deactivate Scanner
ACC -> ACC: refresh()
deactivate ACC

== 方式三：无参构造后手动注册或扫描 ==

Client -> ACC: new AnnotationConfigApplicationContext()
Client -> ACC: register(AppConfig.class)
ACC -> Reader: register(componentClasses)
Reader -> Registry: registerBeanDefinition(beanName, abd)
Client -> ACC: scan("com.example")
ACC -> Scanner: scan(basePackages)
Scanner -> Registry: registerBeanDefinition(beanName, bd)
Client -> ACC: refresh()

note over ACC
三种入口最终都会走到 refresh()。
register(...) 只把显式类注册成 BeanDefinition；
scan(...) 先扫描包路径，把候选组件注册成 BeanDefinition；
真正解析 @Configuration / @Bean / @Import 等是在 refresh() 中完成。
end note

== refresh 阶段：触发注解配置类解析 ==

ACC -> AAC: refresh()
activate AAC
AAC -> AAC: prepareRefresh()
AAC -> AAC: obtainFreshBeanFactory()
AAC -> AAC: prepareBeanFactory(beanFactory)
AAC -> AAC: postProcessBeanFactory(beanFactory)
AAC -> Delegate: invokeBeanFactoryPostProcessors(beanFactory, getBeanFactoryPostProcessors())
activate Delegate
Delegate -> Registry: getBeanNamesForType(BeanDefinitionRegistryPostProcessor)
Registry --> Delegate: org.springframework.context.annotation.internalConfigurationAnnotationProcessor
Delegate -> CCPP: postProcessBeanDefinitionRegistry(registry)
activate CCPP
CCPP -> CCPP: processConfigBeanDefinitions(registry)

CCPP -> Parser: new ConfigurationClassParser(...)
activate Parser
loop parse candidates until no new config classes
	CCPP -> Parser: parse(candidates)
	Parser -> Parser: processConfigurationClass(configClass)
	Parser -> Parser: doProcessConfigurationClass(...)
	Parser -> Parser: processMemberClasses(...)
	Parser -> Parser: processPropertySource(...)
	Parser -> Parser: processComponentScans(...)
	Parser -> Parser: processImports(...)
	Parser -> Parser: retrieveBeanMethodMetadata(@Bean)
end
Parser --> CCPP: Set<ConfigurationClass>
deactivate Parser

CCPP -> ConfigReader: new ConfigurationClassBeanDefinitionReader(...)
activate ConfigReader
ConfigReader -> ConfigReader: loadBeanDefinitions(configClasses)
loop each ConfigurationClass
	ConfigReader -> Registry: register imported/config class BeanDefinition
	ConfigReader -> Registry: register @Bean method BeanDefinition
	ConfigReader -> Registry: register ImportBeanDefinitionRegistrar definitions
	ConfigReader -> Registry: register imported resources definitions
end
deactivate ConfigReader
CCPP -> Registry: enhance @Configuration classes with CGLIB
deactivate CCPP
Delegate -> Delegate: invokeBeanFactoryPostProcessors(...)
deactivate Delegate

AAC -> Delegate: registerBeanPostProcessors(beanFactory)
AAC -> AAC: initMessageSource()
AAC -> AAC: initApplicationEventMulticaster()
AAC -> AAC: onRefresh()
AAC -> AAC: registerListeners()
AAC -> AAC: finishBeanFactoryInitialization(beanFactory)
AAC -> Registry: preInstantiateSingletons()
AAC -> AAC: finishRefresh()
deactivate AAC

note over CCPP, ConfigReader
ConfigurationClassPostProcessor 是注解启动链路的核心：
1. 先找出候选配置类
2. 解析 @ComponentScan、@Import、@ImportResource、@Bean 等元数据
3. 把解析结果继续注册为 BeanDefinition
4. 对 full @Configuration 类做 CGLIB 增强，保证 @Bean 方法调用语义
end note

== 关键角色 ==

note over Reader
AnnotatedBeanDefinitionReader
负责显式 register(Class...)：
把传入 Class 包装为 AnnotatedGenericBeanDefinition 并注册。
end note

note over Scanner
ClassPathBeanDefinitionScanner
负责 scan(String...)：
按包路径扫描 @Component 派生注解类，
例如 @Component、@Service、@Repository、@Controller。
end note

note over Registry
BeanDefinitionRegistry / DefaultListableBeanFactory
是 BeanDefinition 的注册中心。
refresh() 后半段会根据这些 BeanDefinition 创建 Bean 实例。
end note

@enduml
